[00:10] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Hi there. Today we\'re going to be showing a demo of the new Tempo MPP agent for the Piñata agents platform which was designed in collaboration with our partner Tempo. Tempo is a purpose-built layer 1 blockchain for payments with a focus on enabling high'

[00:23] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'throughput. Lowcost transactions for any use case. The machine payments protocol or MPPP for short is a protocol which enables machine to machine payments'

[00:35] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'across the internet for various services. So instead of requiring a login, services built with the MPPP protocol can accept payments through tempo for each action taken. This allows agents to pay for services quickly and'

[00:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'easily without the overhead of traditional signup flows. The Tempo MPP directory is a marketplace of paid APIs and services available via MPPP. Today\'s demo will showcase an agent that'

[01:01] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'comes bundled with the Tempo wallet and then also showcase how it can be used to discover, compare, and pay for services in the Tempo MPP directory. This agent can be deployed in just a few clicks today by going to Piñata\'s agent'

[01:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'platform. Let\'s go ahead and get started. So, the first thing we\'re going to need to do is come to agents.piñata.cloud and we\'re going to click on create your first agent.'

[01:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'From here, you can see that we\'re in an agent creation assistant. We have a few options. We can either create a custom agent or we can click on browse templates to check out a few pre-built'

[01:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'agents from our partners. Because we\'re demoing the Tempo MPP wallet agent today, we\'re going to click on browse templates. From here, you can see all of the templates that we have from our various'

[01:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'partners. As mentioned, we\'re going to click on agent with MPP wallet because that\'s what we\'re demoing today. We can read a little bit more about the agent. We can see here it\'s an AI agent. It comes preconfigured with the Tempo'

[02:03] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'wallet. It\'s going to discover, compare, and pay for services in the Tempo MPP directory. So, you have a ton of different tools that your agent can choose from. It\'s going to go out, discover, compare, contrast based on'

[02:16] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'what you\'ve asked it to do. And once it\'s found the services that match what you need, it\'s going to get the prices. It\'s going to pay for those services to be done. And then it\'s just going to do its job. And it\'ll come back once it\'s'

[02:28] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'finished. That\'s really all we need. So, let\'s go ahead and click deploy this agent. Okay. So, on this page, you can see we have the connection set up where we\'re going to connect to an AI provider. For'

